src:
Ronaldova priateľka bola príliš sexy: Keby ten gombík povolil, bolo by zle
Georgina odhalila aj hornú, aj spodnú časť svojho tela.
04 Nov 2019, 11:30 by zv
Európske hudobné ceny MTV sú rozdané. V poradí 26. ročník tohto prestížneho podujatia sa konal v španielskej Seville a pre mnohých prinieslo hneď niekoľko prekvapení. Najsexy vystúpenie večera aj zoznam všetkých ocenených nájdete TU.
Na červenom koberci sa objavili známejšie aj menej známe osobnosti, ktoré sa snažili zaujať outfitom, aby nezostali nepovšimnuté. A podarilo sa. Veľmi pútavo sa obliekla aj Georgina Rodriguez, ktorá prišla na odovzdávanie cien spolu s Cristianom Ronaldom.
Futbalistova budúca manželka mala na sebe asymetrické šaty, ktoré čo-to odhaľovali hore aj dole a keby sa jej jeden gombík rozopol, trapas by bol na svete.
FOTKY NÁJDETE V GALÉRII.
text:
Ronald's girlfriend was too sexy: If the button was released, it would be wrong
Georgina revealed both the upper and lower parts of her body.
04 Nov 2019, 11:30 by Vol
The European MTV Music Awards are given away. The 26th edition of this prestigious event took place in Seville, Spain, and brought many surprises to many. You can find the highest performances of the evening and a list of all the awards here.
Famous and lesser-known personalities appeared on the red carpet, trying to capture the outfit so as not to go unnoticed. And we did. Georgina Rodriguez, who arrived at the awards ceremony with Cristian Ronald, also dressed in a very engaging way.
The football player's future wife wore asymmetrical dresses, which revealed both up and down, and if her button were broken apart, the trapas would be born.
PHOTOS YOU CAN FIND IN THE GALLERY.
